    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#pacho1827"/>, pl. <citedRange>LXVI.6</citedRange></bibl>
                    whence <bibl><ptr target="#CIG"/> <citedRange>5163</citedRange></bibl>; 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SGDI"/> <citedRange>4864</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#farag-jmr1978-1979"/>, p. 232, n. <citedRange>1.c.1</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>37.1679, 1</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>078100</citedRange></bibl>.
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#applebaum1962"/>, pp. <citedRange>34-35</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-65046"><name nymRef="#Μνασιστράτα">Μνασιστράτα</name></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Δωριεύς">Δωριεύς</name></persName>
                    <lb n="3"/><space quantity="2" unit="character"/> <persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Φερώι">Φερώι</name></persName>    

	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p>
                    <app loc="1"><lem resp="#farag-jmr1978-1979">Μνασιστράτα</lem>
                        <rdg resp="#CIG">Μνασιστ<unclear>ρά</unclear>τα</rdg>
                        <rdg resp="#pacho1827"><orig>μνασισιλτα</orig></rdg> 
                    </app>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <app loc="2"><lem resp="#farag-jmr1978-1979">Δωριεύς</lem>
                        <rdg resp="#applebaum1962"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ωριευς</rdg>
                        <rdg resp="#CIG">Ἀσοριεύς</rdg>
                        <rdg resp="#pacho1827"><orig>ασοριευσ</orig></rdg>
                    </app>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <app loc="3"><lem resp="#SGDI #farag-jmr1978-1979">Φερώι</lem>
                        <rdg resp="#CIG"><orig>Φει<unclear>ώ</unclear></orig></rdg>
                        <rdg resp="#pacho1827"><orig>φειωι</orig></rdg> 
                        <rdg resp="#applebaum1962"><note>this line not mentioned</note></rdg>
                    </app>
                </p>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p> Mnasistrata. Dôrieus. Phérô.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p> Mnasistrata. Dorieus. Phero.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p> Mnasistrata. Dorieus. Pherò.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>Line 2 was added later on, as shown by the lettering.</p>
             <p>The woman's name <foreign xml:lang="grc">Φερώι</foreign> was rightly guessed from Pacho's copy by Hiller von Gärtringen for Blass in <bibl><ptr target="#SGDI"/></bibl>, as already mentioned by 
             <bibl><ptr target="#masson1967"/>, p. <citedRange>227</citedRange>, footnote 12</bibl>, which was ignored by <bibl><ptr target="#farag-jmr1978-1979"/></bibl>. We have now three further occurrences of this name in Cyrene.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
    </text>
